I was patrolling ff.net and noticed that my reviews were not posted on
some stories and the site is constantly too busy for searches (various
times for the past 2 days now)...in fact I was re-reading "Yasou"
http://www.fanfiction.net/read.php?storyid=1775744 and I tried
re-posting a review and there was a new message "busy" message that too.

Sooo...

Phil, will Sano ever be more than a brown-eyed puppy waiting at home
for his master?  I mean really your brand of yaoi is sooo adorable :)

Why am I not surprised that you managed to tie in this story with Sagara?
